 upon a time there was a young girl who lived in a village near the forest.  Every morning she would go and pick berries, which she would sell in the market.  One morning she was out gathering berries and a wolf happened to come along.  The wolf said to her, "I will eat you if you don't do exactly as I say."  She was frightened and tried to run away, but the wolf kept on running faster than she did.  He soon overtook her
